source.name: Annual Survey of Public-Employee Retirement Systems (State- and Locally-Administered Pensions)
source.description: The Annual Survey of Public-Employee Retirement Systems (State- and Locally-Administered Pensions) provides revenues, expenditures, financial assets, and membership information for defined-benefit public employee retirement systems. Data are shown for individual retirement systems as well as at the national, state, and local level by state.
